About this hotel

In a traditional Moorish mansion amid 8 hectares of olive groves, this elegant hotel features views of the Atlas Mountains. It's 9 km from Bahia Palace, 10 km from the lively Jama El f’na Market and 16 km from Marrakesh Menara Airport.

    About this hotel

    In a traditional Moorish mansion amid 8 hectares of olive groves, this elegant hotel features views of the Atlas Mountains. It's 9 km from Bahia Palace, 10 km from the lively Jama El f’na Market and 16 km from Marrakesh Menara Airport. …

    Rustic rooms with wood decor come with Wi-Fi, sitting areas and garden views. Some have balconies or patios. Suites add separate living rooms.

    There's an open-air restaurant, and an internal courtyard that has a fountain, plus a rooftop terrace, a hot tub, and lush gardens with pools and sunloungers. A spa area with a sauna and a hammam offers massages. Breakfast, airport transfers and parking are available.
